public abstract class AbstractDataColumn
extends org.apache.wicket.extensions.markup.html.repeater.data.table.AbstractColumn<Event>
implements IDataColumn

Default implementation of IDataColumn. Expects the column header to be a simple string. Implementations can define a getItemString() method, and this class will by default return that string as a Label object for use in DataTables.
